Package com.camerontec.util.datamodel.expression.compiler.tree

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExpressionTreeVisitor
    Classes implementing this interface are used to visit the nodes in an ExpressionTree.
    Visitable
    Interface implemented by whichever class that needs to be visited by an ExpressionTreeVisitor as per the Visitor design pattern.
